k:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 24, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104pnk1665702798293.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pnk1665702798293.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/pnk1665702798293.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"pnk1665702798293\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Button Texts\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Use this editor to edit texts for the buttons which appear on panels for the current language setup.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"pnk1665702798293__p_d8441e1_d8442e1_d8443e1\">The text is displayed with panel buttons that use this language setup. The list of actions shows the Uniface structure editor functions and other commands that can be defined as buttons on panels.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"pnk1665702798293__section_tdf_hkj_5cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d889327e58\">Fields</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"pnk1665702798293__ul_bgk_hkj_5cc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pnk1665702798293__li_d3947e1_d3948e1_d3949e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Action</span>—names of Uniface\n               structure editor functions and other commands that can be defined as buttons and\n               displayed on the panels using the current language setup. This field is read-only. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"pnk1665702798293__li_d3950e1_d3951e1_d3952e1\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Button Text</span>—text of panel\n               button. <p class=\"p\" id=\"pnk1665702798293__p_d8447e1_d8448e1_d8449e1\">For example, the default button text for\n                  ACCEPT is <code class=\"ph codeph\">Store</code>, but you can change this to\n                  <code class=\"ph codeph\">Save</code>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cqe1665702873537.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Language Setups</a><p>A language setup is a collection of definitions that specify the texts and formatting of language-related data that may be visible in the user interface of a desktop application.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530980\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2530980\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Button Texts Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 24, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Button Texts Use this editor to edit texts for the buttons which appear on panels for the current language setup. The text is displayed with panel buttons that use this language setup. The list of actions shows the Uniface structure editor functions and other commands that can be defined as buttons on panels. Fields Action —names of Uniface structure editor functions and other commands that can be defined as buttons and displayed on the panels using the current language setup. This field is read-only. Button Text —text of panel button. For example, the default button text for ACCEPT is Store , but you can change this to Save . Related Links Language Setups A language setup is a collection of definitions that specify the texts and formatting of language-related data that may be visible in the user interface of a desktop application. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}